body:
### About
Watch the weather forecast simply from [Livedoor Weather Web Service](http://weather.livedoor.com/weather_hacks/webservice.html) API

### Usage
Install and execute ```weather``` command with your zipcode

```
$ gem install weather_hacker
$ weather 6900261
```

　

```
2012-04-15
{
        "weather" => "晴れ",
    "temperature" => {
        "max" => "18",
        "min" => "5"
    }
}

2012-04-16
{
        "weather" => "晴のち曇",
    "temperature" => {
        "max" => "18",
        "min" => "2"
    }
}

2012-04-17
{
        "weather" => "曇り",
    "temperature" => {
        "max" => "17",
        "min" => "9"
    }
}
```

### Require
Ruby >= 1.9.2

### Other
Feel free to create issues or report bugs.
